INSTRUCTIONS:
- Review all fields in BOTH documents above
- Any field whose value appears in lost document — do not use as an answer
- Generate questions that can only be answered by someone who has personally held or owns this specific document
- Prioritise specific sub-fields e.g specific name positions, partial document number digits, specific address components, additional fields
- If there are not enough non-visible fields to generate {{maxSecurityQuestions}} questions — generate fewer, do not invent questions
- Plain text only — no HTML encoding, no special characters, no markdown in questions or answers

Return ONLY a valid JSON array. No markdown. No explanation. No preamble.

Schema:
[
  {
    "question": string,
    "answer": string
  }
]